General.Name: Learning 2 Sleep L2S AB
General.Description: Learning 2 Sleep L2S AB (publ), a digital sleep clinic, focuses on the provision of cognitive behavioral therapy treatment services for care of sleep problems through a digital platform. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Malmo, Sweden.
